001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 73,
009    displayName = "Pump Settings Parameter Change",
010    usedByTidepool = true
011)
012public class ParamChangePumpSettingsHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
013    
014    private int modification;
015    private int status;
016    private int lowInsulinThreshold;
017    private int cannulaPrimeSize;
018    private int isFeatureLocked;
019    private int autoShutdownEnabled;
020    private int oledTimeout;
021    private int autoShutdownDuration;
022    
023    public ParamChangePumpSettingsHistoryLog() {}
024    public ParamChangePumpSettingsHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int modification, int status, int lowInsulinThreshold, int cannulaPrimeSize, int isFeatureLocked, int autoShutdownEnabled, int oledTimeout, int autoShutdownDuration) {
025        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
026        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, modification, status, lowInsulinThreshold, cannulaPrimeSize, isFeatureLocked, autoShutdownEnabled, oledTimeout, autoShutdownDuration);
027        this.modification = modification;
028        this.status = status;
029        this.lowInsulinThreshold = lowInsulinThreshold;
030        this.cannulaPrimeSize = cannulaPrimeSize;
031        this.isFeatureLocked = isFeatureLocked;
032        this.autoShutdownEnabled = autoShutdownEnabled;
033        this.oledTimeout = oledTimeout;
034        this.autoShutdownDuration = autoShutdownDuration;
035        
036    }
037
038    public ParamChangePumpSettingsHistoryLog(int modification, int status, int lowInsulinThreshold, int cannulaPrimeSize, int isFeatureLocked, int autoShutdownEnabled, int oledTimeout, int autoShutdownDuration) {
039        this(0, 0, modification, status, lowInsulinThreshold, cannulaPrimeSize, isFeatureLocked, autoShutdownEnabled, oledTimeout, autoShutdownDuration);
040    }
041
042    public int typeId() {
043        return 73;
044    }
045
046    /**
047     * <table border="1">
048     * <caption>Parsed fields for ParamChangePumpSettingsHistoryLog:</caption>
049     * <tr><td><code>modification</code></td><td><code>raw[10]</code></td></tr>
050     * <tr><td><code>status</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 12)</code></td></tr>
051     * <tr><td><code>lowInsulinThreshold</code></td><td><code>raw[14]</code></td></tr>
052     * <tr><td><code>cannulaPrimeSize</code></td><td><code>raw[15]</code></td></tr>
053     * <tr><td><code>isFeatureLocked</code></td><td><code>raw[16]</code></td></tr>
054     * <tr><td><code>autoShutdownEnabled</code></td><td><code>raw[17]</code></td></tr>
055     * <tr><td><code>oledTimeout</code></td><td><code>raw[19]</code></td></tr>
056     * <tr><td><code>autoShutdownDuration</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 20)</code></td></tr>
057     * </table>
058     */
059    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
060        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
061        this.cargo = raw;
062        parseBase(raw);
063        this.modification = raw[10];
064        this.status = Bytes.readShort(raw, 12);
065        this.lowInsulinThreshold = raw[14];
066        this.cannulaPrimeSize = raw[15];
067        this.isFeatureLocked = raw[16];
068        this.autoShutdownEnabled = raw[17];
069        this.oledTimeout = raw[19];
070        this.autoShutdownDuration = Bytes.readShort(raw, 20);
071        
072    }
073
074    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int modification, int status, int lowInsulinThreshold, int cannulaPrimeSize, int isFeatureLocked, int autoShutdownEnabled, int oledTimeout, int autoShutdownDuration) {
075        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
076            new byte[]{73, 0},
077            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
078            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
079            new byte[]{ (byte) modification }, 
080            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(status), 
081            new byte[]{ (byte) lowInsulinThreshold }, 
082            new byte[]{ (byte) cannulaPrimeSize }, 
083            new byte[]{ (byte) isFeatureLocked }, 
084            new byte[]{ (byte) autoShutdownEnabled }, 
085            new byte[]{ (byte) oledTimeout }, 
086            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(autoShutdownDuration)));
087    }
088    public int getModification() {
089        return modification;
090    }
091    public int getStatus() {
092        return status;
093    }
094    public int getLowInsulinThreshold() {
095        return lowInsulinThreshold;
096    }
097    public int getCannulaPrimeSize() {
098        return cannulaPrimeSize;
099    }
100    public int getIsFeatureLocked() {
101        return isFeatureLocked;
102    }
103    public int getAutoShutdownEnabled() {
104        return autoShutdownEnabled;
105    }
106    public int getOledTimeout() {
107        return oledTimeout;
108    }
109    public int getAutoShutdownDuration() {
110        return autoShutdownDuration;
111    }
112    
113}
